## ğŸ”” Real-Time Feedback

Helify provides live guidance:

| Color | Meaning |
|------|--------|
| Cyan | Correct movement |
| Yellow | Warning |
| Red | Unsafe or invalid |

These appear as floating notifications while exercising.

